{
  "stem": "13623.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Every morning when we get up those few days that we were there, every morning when we get up for [NON-ENGLISH], that counting and standing in line is called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When we get out, it was like 4 or 5 AM.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was still dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The stars were still out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We saw people on the-- we were surrounded with electric wire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Some people that couldn't take it just, during the night, walked out, and they grabbed the wire.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In the morning, we used to see them in different positions where they committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They didn't-- they-- they just-- they couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We weren't in Auschwitz too long, which was lucky for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because, otherwise, I probably wouldn't make it, 'cause that was a bad place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They moved us to a railroad again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We come into the railroad station and same cars as the cars-- same type of cars as the cars that brought us there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Only, now, we're all in prisoner clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And everybody has to sit down, open your legs, and another man sits in front of you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The other man opens his legs like that and another man sits in front of you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we're all loaded tight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In the middle, there is all the room that you have for the guards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The guards are [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yugoslavian-speaking [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Croatian SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They spoke Yugoslavian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They probably couldn't even speak German well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But they were SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Aside from their weapons, they had a long stick that would reach to any end of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They tell us only one person can get up at a time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "If more than one person gets up, you get shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We're in the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
